<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.7.3">
<l>miṉṉukko ṭiyumōrveṇ ṭiṅkaḷum cūḻpari vēṭamumāy</l>
<l>piṉṉaṟṟu laṅkumara cilaiyumpī taka<supplied>c</supplied>ciṟ ṟāṭaiyōṭum</l>
<l>miṉṉiṟpo lintatōrkār mukilpōlak kaḻuttiṉiṟ kāṟaiyoṭum</l>
<l>taṉṉiṟpo lintaviru ṭīkēcaṉ taḷarnaṭai naṭavāṉō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The pipal leaf ornament that shines on a braid [around his waist]</l>
<l rend="indent">along with [his] golden smallcloth</l>
<l>having become the streak of lightning, the white moon, and the surrounding halo,</l>
<l>along with the gold necklace on [his] neck</l>
<l rend="indent">[being] like a black cloud that shines with lightning,</l>
<l>will Hṛṣīkeśa who shines in him not come with a tottering walk?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
